171 A.3d 1265 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. SHIQUAN D. BELLAMY, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-218 SeptTerm 2017

079390 October 20, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003369-13 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
